div.div:
Akihabara is the center of the universe for the coolest hobbies and quirkiest amusements. In the spring of 1999, bright-eyed Nagomi Wahira moves there with dreams of joining a maid caf. She quickly dons an apron at caf Ton Tokoton, AKA the Pig Hut. But adjusting to life in bustling Akihabara isnt as easy as serving tea and delighting customers. Paired with the dour Ranko who never seems to smile, Nagomi must do her best to elevate the Pig Hut over all other maid cafs vying for top ranking. Along the way shell slice out a place for herself amid the frills and thrills of life at the Pig Hut. Just when Nagomis dreams are within her grasp, she discovers not everything is as it seems amid the maid cafs of Akihabara.
(Source: HIDIVE)
The sixth season of Boku no Hero Academia.
